163
00:15:01,899 --> 00:15:02,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

164
00:15:02,220 --> 00:15:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio poticaj koji si ti u svojoj slobodi

165
00:15:06,039 --> 00:15:08,620
