166
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:10,259
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, kao trudnice.

167
00:15:10,259 --> 00:15:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ja imamo mnogo trudnica Bogu fala u zajednici

168
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:14,500
