178
00:15:33,860 --> 00:15:36,240
[SPEAKER_01] Svaka karizma, osim dara i jezika,

179
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] je za izgradnju crkve.

180
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] Tu nema šale.

181
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:44,320
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte se šaliti s Bogom.

182
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ćete doći jedan dan pred njega

183
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] i on će dao, ja sam ti dao to i to.

184
00:15:48,519 --> 00:15:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] Šta si učinio s tim?

185
00:15:50,039 --> 00:15:53,200
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi su dobili dar evangelizacije,

186
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,480
