187
00:15:55,759 --> 00:15:57,080
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako ga nisi razvijao,

188
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,379
[SPEAKER_01] što si učinio?

189
00:15:58,379 --> 00:16:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bio si kao onaj zliji i ljeni sluga

190
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:01,440
[SPEAKER_01] koji je zakopao dar.

191
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,320
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, znam da si ti strog.

192
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,240
[SPEAKER_01] Pa sam ga zakopao na sigurno.

193
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] Taj sluga je kažnjen.

194
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:14,779
